title: Episode 336: Jimmy On the Train (Feat. Jim Jones)
itunes:title: Episode 336: Jimmy On the Train (Feat. Jim Jones)
description:
Rapper/entrepreneur, Jim Jones joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote his Gangsta Grillz Mixtape, dropping 1/14/22, his upcoming rap album, his Spanish album, AND all of his businesses! Jim, Angela, and Steph bring out their inner New York when discussing their childhood dating life in NYC, Jim and Gigi reminisce on wild strip club nights in the early 2000's, Jim breaks down how he lost his virginity, and much more. Enjoy!
